      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPRING MISTY (1) is a fast beginner who has shown good improvement at her last two starts, breaking through last time at this track over 352m. Great chance to get the job done again. BIG REVEAL (3) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by half a length at this track in a handy 19.78 beating GOLDSTAR HARMONY. Likely to be in the finish. GOLDSTAR HARMONY (5) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind BIG REVEAL (19.82) in a P5. Has the early speed to give a sight. Will give a great sight again. REVA TWIST (2) is a last start winner who can measure up again.",
